Introduction

Yuki is a Japanese singer, dancer, rapper and actress signed with RBW Entertainment. She is the Main Rapper, Lead Dancer and Sub Vocalist of the girl group PURPLE KISS. She is also the Main Rapper, Dancer, Vocalist and Maknae of the project girl group EL7Z UP.

She debuted with PURPLE KISS on March 15, 2021, with the mini album “INTO VIOLET”, with the title track “Ponzona”.

On April 24, 2023, she participated in the survival show Queendom Puzzle and finished in 3rd place earning her spot in the project girl group EL7Z UP. She made her debut with EL7Z UP on September 14, 2023, with their first mini album “7+UP”, with the title track “CHEEKY”.
